
= The Remakery is an innovative new community project in north Brixton. The co-operative is in the process of renovating a disused underground carpark to create '''a new co-working and educational space for making stuff out of waste materials'''. 

URL = http://remakery.posterous.com/


=Description=

"The Remakery will provide a co-working space and collaborative network for local enterprises creating products and opportunities from waste. We are currently under-going a community self-build process and are open for volunteers! Opening in Autumn 2013."


